{"tid":1596794,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"8個月床戰50男 83歲嬤狂言：沒人不想屌我","createTime":"2019-09-26T16:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T06:56:08.000Z","uid":225846,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0fc783b568ca0fd9482046dfbc17ff91b85aa973","tid":1596794,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2019/09/06/20190906103457-0e8cd05a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F06%2F20190906103457-0e8cd05a.jpg&h=2390f09f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國一名83歲的阿嬤，雖然年紀較長，但她的生活卻過得很「性」福。 圖／翻攝至Hattie Retroage Instagram<br />\n「年老色衰」、「歲月是年輕的殺手」這些話套在這個人身上一點都不適用！美國一名83歲的阿嬤，雖然年紀較長，但她的生活卻過得很「性」福，頻繁使用交友軟體的她，時常在網上與小鮮肉聊天，這8個月來已經床戰50多名男子，她甚至狂言從未遇過有人是不想跟她做愛的。<br />\n <br />\n根據太陽報報導指出，這名83歲阿嬤名叫海蒂（Hattie Retroage）向外媒透露，自己每周都要在交友軟體上約會，和至少3名男子出去玩，雖然年事已高，但她仍對自己的姿色相當有信心，甚至狂言「我從未遇到一個男人是不想跟我做愛的。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2019/09/06/20190906103454-a6279817.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F06%2F20190906103454-a6279817.jpg&h=77780648&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n狂言從未遇過有人是不想跟她做愛的。 圖／翻攝至Hattie Retroage Instagram<br />\n<br />\n海蒂表示自己通常都跟年齡約在50歲左右的男生約會，也曾經在報紙上刊登廣告，希望尋找35歲以上的床伴，此舉當時遭到許多人撻伐。<br />\n <br />\n不過她也強調，自己不是每次都會跟約會對象纏綿，「如果我們出去喝酒，然後那個氛圍又對的話，我們就會去我的公寓；但如果氣氛不對，就會互相離開。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2019/09/06/20190906103455-dd7253bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F06%2F20190906103455-dd7253bf.jpg&h=a0195f68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海蒂強調，自己不是每次都會跟約會對象纏綿。 圖／翻攝至Hattie Retroage Instagram<br />\n<br />\n最後，海蒂也給更年期女性一些建議，她說「我給大家的建議就是自己解決，無論你是否願意，都必須讓你的引擎保持運轉、保持活力。」"},{"pid":"bd42e326fdd0e0aee5e62f3e3af1bc6bf4500d26","tid":1596794,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:01:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ddd41376d659cdb6234951d3280bd2f357b6c94e","tid":1596794,"uid":263219,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:01:22.000Z","msg":"真係keep得好wor"},{"pid":"0e82d908637c0cf854306b2742b1ff31e2641363","tid":1596794,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd42e326fdd0e0aee5e62f3e3af1bc6bf4500d26","tid":1596794,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:01:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:02:03.000Z","msg":"俾你增加下人生閱歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1c06286fab0d7bbc6ca3dc656082b682b4fe9ac","tid":1596794,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:03:06.000Z","msg":"唔識欣賞"},{"pid":"f59bf2b257f9127edb9d9c1799d8ddc138d35cfb","tid":1596794,"uid":282777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T16:13:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c9de6aa7080e5d6c82fad3e59e6fe1f55c3032d","tid":1596794,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T17:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a3063c87477dc3ebea5b58f04fdb7abf0ba2b2","tid":1596794,"uid":225846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T06:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086c6d59ece7435e45103732e218e463663e0973","tid":1596794,"uid":58413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T06:56:08.000Z","msg":"想嘔"}]}